title: 400. Andy & DJ CTI: George Floyd's Family Sues Kanye West, Boston University Creates New Strain & Steele Dossier Source Acquitted
itunes:title: 400. Andy & DJ CTI: George Floyd's Family Sues Kanye West, Boston University Creates New Strain & Steele Dossier Source Acquitted
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss George Floyd's family's plan to sue Kanye West for $250 million over comments about his death, Boson University's lab creating a new deadly COVID strain with an 80% kill rate, and the primary source for the Steele Dossier acquitted of four counts of lying to the FBI.
